# Smart Pet Feeder & Monitor

## Overview
An IoT-based system that allows users to monitor and feed pets remotely using internet connectivity. :contentReference[oaicite:11]{index=11}

---

## Features
- Remote feeding control
- Live video streaming
- Internet-based monitoring

